要自己上網google係咁睇wiki同youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nasso同u最大分別:<br />\n<br />\nasso都仲會照住你，比你靠勤力拎高GPA。<br />\n<br />\nU班仆街理撚得你死，講一次就算，唔明自己查書，自生自滅。想拎高GPA就要睇熟本reference book + 睇你有冇天份。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n各有各辛苦 不過我呢邊就chur完玩都玩得唔安落 睇你點睇啦"},{"pid":"a119a1685185c278f89f77bcba26a90bc042842c","tid":49432,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>12/25 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拎到12分唔會拉到成科fail啦 仲未計拉curve</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仲有得追 我試個c左份assignment 成科都係A</blockquote><br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3685493f794d3f07cf869d8f22665a55561e5779","tid":49432,"uid":28471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:24:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>asso重點係   拎 source <br />\n包括past asignment midterm<br />\nasso d導師係超懶  個個sem d野 勁似  <br />\n得source 有哂 model ans 贏左9 成<br />\nfinal份野  成日有一半copy mid term<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你死chur靠堅明   答卷出黎分分鐘輸比人地有source 下下答 model ans</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係間間cc都有source/ past paper 認真</blockquote><br />\n無source 輸一半  點會無  實有同學 果科讀過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果靠純選    要 chur 就chur d功課 <br />\n<br />\n再講一次  asso lecturer係超懶    final抄 mid term  , mid term就抄功課  <br />\n而且除左懶  其實一半可能係怕學生 太屎   答出黎顯得佢地教得廢    比學校插</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我啲lecturer 全部都好有心機教 出卷跟時事出 點都會update 真係無past paper 我呢度唔係hkcc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f74834c82af0646c3268b43c37a0bff880e0c98","tid":49432,"uid":4946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:26:13.000Z","msg":"成日聽人講話入大學之後大把好日子過，根本係一個騙局，一個sem同考DSE無分別，考五科，仲要科科都多concept嘢，如果食晒啲notes可以