ets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nasso同u最大分別:<br />\n<br />\nasso都仲會照住你，比你靠勤力拎高GPA。<br />\n<br />\nU班仆街理撚得你死，講一次就算，唔明自己查書，自生自滅。想拎高GPA就要睇熟本reference book + 睇你有冇天份。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAsso勤力好易拎A 至少都B+<br />\n入到大學先見真章 真係好講天份 只求grad:<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebeea93f144b97cd65a632cd8bbbbd9936bfaa83","tid":49432,"uid":72093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T20:24:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n3.8x</blockquote><br />\n屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁杞人憂天啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n壓力太大會影響發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你有3.8幾基本上都半隻腳入左u<br />\ninterview表現好啲就ok</blockquote><br />\n好明po主 個重點唔係淨係要入u而係入到自己想入嗰科 <br />\n而我嗰科爆完4都未必入到 爆到4係必要條件 <br />\nasso唔難 最難係心理因素 成兩年無得放鬆 嗰種自己俾自己嘅心理壓力好撚大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：3.8 入唔撚到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAsso最難係心理因素 因為份份assignment 都好緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142d4725b631ccdd30a8762fd51b4bc899ebf890","tid":49432,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T20:43:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>asso啲野簡單喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n考試前幾日chur下都有靚grade<br />\nhea上堂 刨返notes就ok<br />\n反而依家上到degree就真係讀撚到嘔<br />\n又要刨reference book <br />\n啲野又冇咁straight forward<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時上堂聽小兩三句可能返到去就睇唔明notes<br />\n要自己上網google係咁睇wiki同youtube<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nasso同u最大分別:<br />\n<br />\nasso都仲會照住你，比你靠勤力拎高GPA。<br />\n<br />\nU班仆街理撚得你死，講一次就算，唔明自己查書，自生自滅。想拎高GPA就